participant_flow.pre_assignment_details:
Randomized participants were stratified by the following 2 parameters:
C-Reactive Protein (CRP) concentration (normal: ≤ 1.5 mg/dl or elevated: > 1.5 mg/dl) from screening;
The Bath Ankylosing Spondylitis Disease Activity Index (BASDAI) score < 6.0 or BASDAI score ≥ 6.0 from baseline.
